column5: Leaving Sat. 7/25 Just wondering how much road const. is gravel between I-falls and Antikokan on Hwy. 11 ? Any big delays ?Thanks Slimerocket
As of last Friday there was none. Road was in good shape.
Update- Hwy-11 is fine, but Hwy-622 back to Clearwater west has about 14-miles of loose gravel. So if you have a nice boat be perparied..
